{"id":14,"date":"2024-03-12T13:24:36","date_gmt":"2024-03-12T13:24:36","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/portfolio\/"},"modified":"2024-04-08T06:37:23","modified_gmt":"2024-04-08T06:37:23","slug":"veille-technologique","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/veille-technologique\/","title":{"rendered":"VEILLE"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull has-background-background-color has-background is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-group-is-layout-5 wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30)\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-content-justification-center is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\">Veille Technologique<\/h2>\n\n\n<style>.wp-block-kadence-spacer.kt-block-spacer-14_7fb83e-55 .kt-block-spacer{height:6px;}.wp-block-kadence-spacer.kt-block-spacer-14_7fb83e-55 .kt-divider{border-top-width:5px;height:1px;border-top-color:#0083ff;width:84%;border-top-style:solid;}<\/style>\n<div class=\"wp-block-kadence-spacer aligncenter kt-block-spacer-14_7fb83e-55\"><div class=\"kt-block-spacer kt-block-spacer-halign-center\"><hr class=\"kt-divider\"\/><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-1 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\"><strong>Qu&rsquo;est ce que la veille technologique ? :<\/strong><\/h3>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignwide is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-group-is-layout-2 wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\">La veille technologique d\u00e9signe le processus syst\u00e9matique de surveillance, de collecte, d&rsquo;analyse et de diffusion d&rsquo;informations relatives aux avanc\u00e9es, aux innovations, et aux \u00e9volutions dans le domaine technologique. Elle vise \u00e0 anticiper les changements, \u00e0 d\u00e9tecter les opportunit\u00e9s et les menaces, ainsi qu&rsquo;\u00e0 rester inform\u00e9 sur les tendances et les nouveaut\u00e9s qui pourraient impacter une entreprise, une industrie ou un domaine d&rsquo;activit\u00e9 sp\u00e9cifique. La veille technologique permet aux organisations de prendre des d\u00e9cisions \u00e9clair\u00e9es, d&rsquo;innover, de rester comp\u00e9titives et de s&rsquo;adapter aux \u00e9volutions rapides du march\u00e9.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\"><strong>Dans le cadre de mon BTS SIO et pour mes futures activit\u00e9s de veille technologique, j\u2019ai utilis\u00e9 deux outils essentiels :<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignwide is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-group-is-layout-3 wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\"><strong>Google Alerts<\/strong>&nbsp;: Cet outil m\u2019a permis de rester inform\u00e9 en temps r\u00e9el des derni\u00e8res actualit\u00e9s technologiques pertinent en m&rsquo;envoyant directement des notifications dans ma bo\u00eete de r\u00e9ception, ce qui m\u2019a aid\u00e9 \u00e0 suivre les sujets qui m\u2019int\u00e9ressent le plus.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"656\" height=\"254\" src=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image_2024-04-01_182129118.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-498\" style=\"width:521px;height:auto\" srcset=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image_2024-04-01_182129118.png 656w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image_2024-04-01_182129118-300x116.png 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 656px) 100vw, 656px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\"><strong>Feedly&nbsp;<\/strong>: J&rsquo;ai opt\u00e9 pour l&rsquo;utilisation de Feedly afin d&rsquo;agr\u00e9ger les flux RSS provenant de divers sites web technologiques. Cette plateforme m&rsquo;a permis de centraliser et d&rsquo;organiser efficacement les derni\u00e8res publications issues de blogs, de forums et d&rsquo;autres sources d&rsquo;actualit\u00e9s que je suivais r\u00e9guli\u00e8rement. Gr\u00e2ce \u00e0 l&rsquo;interface conviviale de Feedly, j&rsquo;ai pu personnaliser mes abonnements et mes pr\u00e9f\u00e9rences de lecture, ce qui a grandement facilit\u00e9 ma consultation quotidienne des informations les plus pertinentes.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"338\" src=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image_2024-04-02_203118966.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-577\" srcset=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image_2024-04-02_203118966.png 1024w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image_2024-04-02_203118966-300x99.png 300w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image_2024-04-02_203118966-768x254.png 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\">Articles de veilles<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\"><strong>Th\u00e8me : Cybers\u00e9curit\u00e9 \/ Fuite de donn\u00e9es \/ AI<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\">Je me tiens inform\u00e9 des derni\u00e8res tendances en mati\u00e8re de fuites de donn\u00e9es et de cybers\u00e9curit\u00e9 afin d&rsquo;analyser les menaces potentielles auxquelles font face les organisations. Mon objectif est de proposer des solutions efficaces pour prot\u00e9ger les informations sensibles et pr\u00e9venir les violations de s\u00e9curit\u00e9.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull has-background-background-color has-background is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-group-is-layout-21 wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30)\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-2 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\" style=\"margin-top:48px\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column has-border-color has-palette-color-1-border-color is-layout-flow wp-container-core-column-is-layout-2 wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"border-width:5px;padding-top:0;padding-right:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0;box-shadow:var(--wp--preset--shadow--sharp)\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full is-resized ext-aspect-landscape\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/img-QYLEpk3kv5IjolDc0SWJWik8.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-732\" style=\"width:209px;height:auto\" srcset=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/img-QYLEpk3kv5IjolDc0SWJWik8.png 1024w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/img-QYLEpk3kv5IjolDc0SWJWik8-300x300.png 300w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/img-QYLEpk3kv5IjolDc0SWJWik8-150x150.png 150w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/img-QYLEpk3kv5IjolDc0SWJWik8-768x768.png 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-flow wp-container-core-group-is-layout-6 wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\" style=\"margin-top:0;padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30)\">\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-foreground-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-33423fac65b31a28e0a56c17b20b5385\" style=\"font-size:clamp(0.984rem, 0.984rem + ((1vw - 0.2rem) * 0.645), 1.5rem);\"><strong>A suivre ?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\"><strong>Date de Publication : ? <\/strong><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column has-border-color has-palette-color-1-border-color is-layout-flow wp-container-core-column-is-layout-3 wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"border-width:5px;padding-top:0;padding-right:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0;box-shadow:var(--wp--preset--shadow--sharp)\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full is-resized ext-aspect-landscape\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/img-QYLEpk3kv5IjolDc0SWJWik8.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-732\" style=\"width:209px;height:auto\" srcset=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/img-QYLEpk3kv5IjolDc0SWJWik8.png 1024w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/img-QYLEpk3kv5IjolDc0SWJWik8-300x300.png 300w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/img-QYLEpk3kv5IjolDc0SWJWik8-150x150.png 150w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/img-QYLEpk3kv5IjolDc0SWJWik8-768x768.png 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-flow wp-container-core-group-is-layout-7 wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\" style=\"margin-top:0;padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30)\">\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-foreground-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-33423fac65b31a28e0a56c17b20b5385\" style=\"font-size:clamp(0.984rem, 0.984rem + ((1vw - 0.2rem) * 0.645), 1.5rem);\"><strong>A suivre ?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\"><strong>Date de Publication : ? <\/strong><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column has-border-color has-palette-color-1-border-color is-layout-flow wp-container-core-column-is-layout-4 wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"border-width:5px;box-shadow:var(--wp--preset--shadow--sharp)\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full is-resized ext-aspect-landscape\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image_2024-04-07_180534373.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-734\" style=\"width:392px;height:auto\" srcset=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image_2024-04-07_180534373.png 1024w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image_2024-04-07_180534373-300x169.png 300w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image_2024-04-07_180534373-768x432.png 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-flow wp-container-core-group-is-layout-8 wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\" style=\"margin-top:0;padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30)\">\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-foreground-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-41b37fad7d4735c983b0ea56c1b3393c\" style=\"font-size:clamp(0.984rem, 0.984rem + ((1vw - 0.2rem) * 0.645), 1.5rem);\"><strong>Qui est la cible favorite des hackers parmi vos coll\u00e8gues<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\"><strong>Date de Publication : 07 avril 2024<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\" style=\"font-size:clamp(14px, 0.875rem + ((1vw - 3.2px) * 0.156), 16px);\"><br>Les pirates informatiques utilisent le \u00ab\u00a0spear phishing\u00a0\u00bb pour cibler sp\u00e9cifiquement des postes cl\u00e9s au sein des entreprises, tels que la direction financi\u00e8re et la comptabilit\u00e9, afin d&rsquo;acc\u00e9der \u00e0 des informations sensibles. L&rsquo;usurpation d&rsquo;identit\u00e9 de cadres est fr\u00e9quente, repr\u00e9sentant plus de 62 % des attaques. Il est crucial de sensibiliser tous les employ\u00e9s aux risques et de renforcer la formation en cybers\u00e9curit\u00e9 pour prot\u00e9ger les entreprises contre ces menaces.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-content-justification-center is-layout-flex wp-container-core-buttons-is-layout-1 wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-fill\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-background-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/www.numerama.com\/cyberguerre\/1666510-qui-est-la-cible-favorite-des-hackers-parmi-vos-collegues.html\" style=\"border-radius:100px;background:linear-gradient(71deg,rgb(0,98,255) 0%,rgb(62,57,96) 100%)\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">En savoir plus<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-3 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\" style=\"margin-top:48px\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column has-border-color has-palette-color-1-border-color is-layout-flow wp-container-core-column-is-layout-5 wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"border-width:5px;padding-top:0;padding-right:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0;box-shadow:var(--wp--preset--shadow--sharp)\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full is-resized ext-aspect-landscape\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"445\" src=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image_2024-04-01_185505104.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-503\" style=\"width:385px;height:auto\" srcset=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image_2024-04-01_185505104.png 800w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image_2024-04-01_185505104-300x167.png 300w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image_2024-04-01_185505104-768x427.png 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-flow wp-container-core-group-is-layout-9 wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\" style=\"margin-top:0;padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30)\">\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-foreground-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-9336414ddda78fca21c1fb0ede7e28f0\" style=\"font-size:clamp(0.984rem, 0.984rem + ((1vw - 0.2rem) * 0.645), 1.5rem);\"><strong>iPhone : la mise \u00e0 jour iOS 17.4 corrige deux failles de s\u00e9curit\u00e9 zero-day d\u00e9j\u00e0 exploit\u00e9es !<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\"><strong>Date de Publication : 06 mars 2024<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\" style=\"font-size:clamp(14px, 0.875rem + ((1vw - 3.2px) * 0.156), 16px);\">Apple a r\u00e9cemment publi\u00e9 des mises \u00e0 jour de s\u00e9curit\u00e9 pour corriger deux failles zero-day exploitant le Kernel et RTKit sur iPhone et iPad. Les vuln\u00e9rabilit\u00e9s CVE-2024-23225 et CVE-2024-23296 permettent \u00e0 un attaquant de contourner les protections de la m\u00e9moire du noyau. Les appareils concern\u00e9s incluent divers mod\u00e8les d&rsquo;iPhone et d&rsquo;iPad. Pour ceux incapables d&rsquo;installer iOS 17.4 ou iPadOS 17.4, une version de correctif est disponible sous iOS 16.7.6 et iPadOS 16.7.6. Il est crucial de mettre \u00e0 jour vos appareils pour \u00e9viter toute exploitation.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-content-justification-center is-layout-flex wp-container-core-buttons-is-layout-2 wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-fill\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-background-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/www.it-connect.fr\/iphone-la-mise-a-jour-ios-17-4-corrige-deux-failles-de-securite-zero-day-deja-exploitees\/\" style=\"border-radius:100px;background:linear-gradient(71deg,rgb(0,98,255) 0%,rgb(62,57,96) 100%)\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">En savoir plus<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column has-border-color has-palette-color-1-border-color is-layout-flow wp-container-core-column-is-layout-6 wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"border-width:5px;padding-right:0;padding-left:0;box-shadow:var(--wp--preset--shadow--sharp)\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full is-resized ext-aspect-landscape\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"750\" src=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image_2024-04-01_184827839.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-501\" style=\"width:345px;height:auto\" srcset=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image_2024-04-01_184827839.png 1200w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image_2024-04-01_184827839-300x188.png 300w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image_2024-04-01_184827839-1024x640.png 1024w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image_2024-04-01_184827839-768x480.png 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-flow wp-container-core-group-is-layout-10 wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\" style=\"margin-top:0;padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30)\">\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-foreground-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-b4ef5861c082b4a04430af85e5a0a05d\" style=\"font-size:clamp(0.984rem, 0.984rem + ((1vw - 0.2rem) * 0.645), 1.5rem);\"><strong>Linux : cette nouvelle faille majeure menace la plupart des utilisateurs de l\u2019OS<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\"><strong>Date de Publication : 01 f\u00e9vrier 202<\/strong>4<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\" style=\"font-size:clamp(14px, 0.875rem + ((1vw - 3.2px) * 0.156), 16px);\">Une faille de s\u00e9curit\u00e9 majeure, CVE-2023-6246, affecte Linux en permettant \u00e0 des utilisateurs d&rsquo;obtenir des privil\u00e8ges root via un d\u00e9bordement de m\u00e9moire tampon dans la fonction syslog() de glibc. Touchant plusieurs distributions, y compris Ubuntu, Debian, Red Hat, CentOS, Fedora et OpenBSD, cette vuln\u00e9rabilit\u00e9 peut \u00eatre exploit\u00e9e pour un contr\u00f4le total sur le syst\u00e8me. Bien que non critique, son exploitation \u00e0 grande \u00e9chelle est probable, car glibc est largement utilis\u00e9e. La mise \u00e0 jour de glibc \u00e0 la version 2.39 est essentielle pour se pr\u00e9munir contre cette menace. Il est crucial d&rsquo;appliquer rapidement les mises \u00e0 jour de s\u00e9curit\u00e9 pour prot\u00e9ger les syst\u00e8mes.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-content-justification-center is-layout-flex wp-container-core-buttons-is-layout-3 wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-fill\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-background-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/www.phonandroid.com\/linux-cette-nouvelle-faille-majeure-menace-la-plupart-des-utilisateurs-de-los.html\" style=\"border-radius:100px;background:linear-gradient(71deg,rgb(0,98,255) 0%,rgb(62,57,96) 100%)\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">En savoir plus<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column has-border-color has-palette-color-1-border-color is-layout-flow wp-container-core-column-is-layout-7 wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"border-width:5px;box-shadow:var(--wp--preset--shadow--sharp)\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full is-resized ext-aspect-landscape\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"445\" src=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image_2024-04-01_182256082.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-499\" style=\"width:392px;height:auto\" srcset=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image_2024-04-01_182256082.png 800w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image_2024-04-01_182256082-300x167.png 300w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image_2024-04-01_182256082-768x427.png 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-flow wp-container-core-group-is-layout-11 wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\" style=\"margin-top:0;padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30)\">\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-foreground-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-7c2081cd6ebd85a769d67a253f285a5b\" style=\"font-size:clamp(0.984rem, 0.984rem + ((1vw - 0.2rem) * 0.645), 1.5rem);\"><strong>Surface d\u2019attaque externe : DNSdumpster, un outil de reconnaissance DNS<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\"><strong>Date de Publication : 16 Janvier 2024<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\" style=\"font-size:clamp(14px, 0.875rem + ((1vw - 3.2px) * 0.156), 16px);\">DNSdumpster est un outil de reconnaissance bas\u00e9 sur le DNS, accessible via dnsdumpster.com, permettant d&rsquo;explorer la surface d&rsquo;attaque externe d&rsquo;un domaine en saisissant le nom de domaine souhait\u00e9. Les r\u00e9sultats comprennent des informations telles que les fournisseurs d&rsquo;infrastructure, la r\u00e9partition g\u00e9ographique des services. Son utilisation doit \u00eatre \u00e9thique et limit\u00e9e aux domaines propres ou avec accord de l&rsquo;administrateur, en tenant compte des cons\u00e9quences potentielles.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-content-justification-center is-layout-flex wp-container-core-buttons-is-layout-4 wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-fill\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-background-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/www.it-connect.fr\/dnsdumpster-un-outil-de-reconnaissance-dns\/\" style=\"border-radius:100px;background:linear-gradient(71deg,rgb(0,98,255) 0%,rgb(62,57,96) 100%)\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">En savoir plus<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-4 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\" style=\"margin-top:48px\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column has-border-color has-palette-color-1-border-color is-layout-flow wp-container-core-column-is-layout-8 wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"border-width:5px;box-shadow:var(--wp--preset--shadow--sharp)\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full is-resized ext-aspect-landscape\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"445\" src=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image_2024-04-01_175834644.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-494\" style=\"width:410px;height:auto\" srcset=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image_2024-04-01_175834644.png 800w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image_2024-04-01_175834644-300x167.png 300w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image_2024-04-01_175834644-768x427.png 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-flow wp-container-core-group-is-layout-13 wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\" style=\"margin-top:0;padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30)\">\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-foreground-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-0cdc8b5b54907fde64cd172c5a544f85\" style=\"font-size:clamp(0.984rem, 0.984rem + ((1vw - 0.2rem) * 0.645), 1.5rem);\"><strong>Cyberattaque, MongoDB alerte sur une violation de donn\u00e9es clients<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\"><strong>Date de Publication : 18 D\u00e9cembre 2023<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\" style=\"font-size:clamp(14px, 0.875rem + ((1vw - 3.2px) * 0.156), 16px);\">Une cyberattaque a vis\u00e9 MongoDB, compromettant certains syst\u00e8mes de l&rsquo;entreprise. L&rsquo;incident a eu lieu le 13 d\u00e9cembre 2023, impliquant un acc\u00e8s non autoris\u00e9 et la compromission de m\u00e9tadonn\u00e9es clients, de donn\u00e9es de contact et de journaux syst\u00e8me d&rsquo;un client sp\u00e9cifique. Jusqu&rsquo;\u00e0 pr\u00e9sent, MongoDB Atlas n&rsquo;a pas \u00e9t\u00e9 affect\u00e9. Les investigations sont en cours pour \u00e9valuer l&rsquo;ampleur des dommages. Pour les mises \u00e0 jour, MongoDB fournit une page d\u00e9di\u00e9e.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-content-justification-center is-layout-flex wp-container-core-buttons-is-layout-5 wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-fill\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-background-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/www.it-connect.fr\/cyberattaque-chez-mongodb-voici-ce-que-lon-sait\/\" style=\"border-radius:100px;background:linear-gradient(71deg,rgb(0,98,255) 0%,rgb(62,57,96) 100%)\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">En savoir plus<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column has-border-color has-palette-color-1-border-color is-layout-flow wp-container-core-column-is-layout-9 wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"border-width:5px;box-shadow:var(--wp--preset--shadow--sharp)\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full is-resized ext-aspect-landscape\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"896\" height=\"598\" src=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image_2024-04-01_155919291.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-485\" style=\"width:345px;height:auto\" srcset=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image_2024-04-01_155919291.png 896w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image_2024-04-01_155919291-300x200.png 300w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image_2024-04-01_155919291-768x513.png 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 896px) 100vw, 896px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-flow wp-container-core-group-is-layout-14 wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\" style=\"margin-top:0;padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30)\">\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-foreground-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-32bbaf777ac31fa37c64fe902c76f927\" style=\"font-size:clamp(0.984rem, 0.984rem + ((1vw - 0.2rem) * 0.645), 1.5rem);\"><strong>L&rsquo;intelligence artificielle face \u00e0 la cybers\u00e9curit\u00e9<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\"><strong>Date de Publication : 28 novembre 2023<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\" style=\"font-size:clamp(14px, 0.875rem + ((1vw - 3.2px) * 0.156), 16px);\">L&rsquo;intelligence artificielle impacte la cybers\u00e9curit\u00e9 en optimisant la d\u00e9tection des menaces, en automatisant les r\u00e9ponses aux incidents et en renfor\u00e7ant la protection contre les cybercriminels. Les mod\u00e8les d&rsquo;IA identifient les vuln\u00e9rabilit\u00e9s et pr\u00e9viennent les menaces telles que l&rsquo;hame\u00e7onnage et les logiciels malveillants. IBM propose des solutions comme IBM Security QRadar, qui utilisent l&rsquo;IA pour renforcer la s\u00e9curit\u00e9 et optimiser le temps des analystes.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-content-justification-center is-layout-flex wp-container-core-buttons-is-layout-6 wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-fill\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-background-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/www.usine-digitale.fr\/article\/l-intelligence-artificielle-face-a-la-cybersecurite.N2198923\" style=\"border-radius:100px;background:linear-gradient(71deg,rgb(0,98,255) 0%,rgb(62,57,96) 100%)\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">En savoir plus<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column has-border-color has-palette-color-1-border-color is-layout-flow wp-container-core-column-is-layout-10 wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"border-width:5px;box-shadow:var(--wp--preset--shadow--sharp)\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full is-resized ext-aspect-landscape\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"896\" height=\"598\" src=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/image_2024-03-31_175847007.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-456\" style=\"width:334px;height:auto\" srcset=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/image_2024-03-31_175847007.png 896w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/image_2024-03-31_175847007-300x200.png 300w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/image_2024-03-31_175847007-768x513.png 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 896px) 100vw, 896px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-flow wp-container-core-group-is-layout-15 wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\" style=\"margin-top:0;padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30)\">\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-foreground-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-07f58c28f618d05728bc8e1056cadcf0\" style=\"font-size:clamp(0.984rem, 0.984rem + ((1vw - 0.2rem) * 0.645), 1.5rem);\"><strong>Deezer victime d&rsquo;une attaque par d\u00e9ni de service<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\"><strong>Date de Publication : 23 octobre 2023<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\" style=\"font-size:clamp(14px, 0.875rem + ((1vw - 3.2px) * 0.156), 16px);\">Deezer a \u00e9t\u00e9 attaqu\u00e9 en DDoS le 22 octobre par le groupe Anonymous Sudan, rendant la plateforme indisponible pendant des heures. Les utilisateurs ont rencontr\u00e9 des probl\u00e8mes de connexion. Une plainte a \u00e9t\u00e9 d\u00e9pos\u00e9e \u00e0 la CNIL pour risque de phishing. Il est recommand\u00e9 de changer les mots de passe. Cela souligne l&rsquo;importance de la s\u00e9curit\u00e9 des donn\u00e9es en ligne.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-content-justification-center is-layout-flex wp-container-core-buttons-is-layout-7 wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-fill\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-background-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/www.usine-digitale.fr\/article\/deezer-victime-d-une-attaque-par-deni-de-service.N2185818\" style=\"border-radius:100px;background:linear-gradient(71deg,rgb(0,98,255) 0%,rgb(62,57,96) 100%)\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">En savoir plus<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-5 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\" style=\"margin-top:48px\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column has-border-color has-palette-color-1-border-color is-layout-flow wp-container-core-column-is-layout-11 wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"border-width:5px;box-shadow:var(--wp--preset--shadow--sharp)\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full is-resized ext-aspect-landscape\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"896\" height=\"598\" src=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/image_2024-03-31_125529858.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-454\" style=\"width:345px;height:auto\" srcset=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/image_2024-03-31_125529858.png 896w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/image_2024-03-31_125529858-300x200.png 300w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/image_2024-03-31_125529858-768x513.png 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 896px) 100vw, 896px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-flow wp-container-core-group-is-layout-17 wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\" style=\"margin-top:0;padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30)\">\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-foreground-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-3670f6a27bb3e09fff37732e825d14b3\" style=\"font-size:clamp(0.984rem, 0.984rem + ((1vw - 0.2rem) * 0.645), 1.5rem);\"><strong>4000 adresses emails et mots de passe d&rsquo;Ile-de-France Mobilit\u00e9s Connect vol\u00e9s par des hackers<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\"><strong>Date de Publication : 09 octobre 2023<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\" style=\"font-size:clamp(14px, 0.875rem + ((1vw - 3.2px) * 0.156), 16px);\">Des&nbsp;<strong>hackers<\/strong>&nbsp;ont r\u00e9ussi \u00e0 mettre la main sur pr\u00e8s de&nbsp;<strong>4 000 adresses e-mails et mots de passe actifs<\/strong>&nbsp;d\u2019utilisateurs du service&nbsp;<strong>Ile-de-France Mobilit\u00e9s Connect<\/strong>. Ils ont ensuite pu se connecter aux comptes associ\u00e9s. Une plainte a \u00e9t\u00e9 d\u00e9pos\u00e9e aupr\u00e8s de la&nbsp;<strong>CNIL<\/strong>&nbsp;en raison du risque de&nbsp;<strong>phishing<\/strong>&nbsp;que cette fuite fait peser sur les utilisateurs concern\u00e9s. Il est vivement recommand\u00e9 aux utilisateurs touch\u00e9s de modifier leur mot de passe pour prot\u00e9ger leurs donn\u00e9es personnelles.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-content-justification-center is-layout-flex wp-container-core-buttons-is-layout-8 wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-fill\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-background-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/www.usine-digitale.fr\/article\/4000-adresses-emails-et-mots-de-passe-d-ile-de-france-mobilites-connect-voles-par-des-hackers.N2180027\" style=\"border-radius:100px;background:linear-gradient(71deg,rgb(0,98,255) 0%,rgb(62,57,96) 100%)\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">En savoir plus<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column has-border-color has-palette-color-1-border-color is-layout-flow wp-container-core-column-is-layout-12 wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"border-width:5px;box-shadow:var(--wp--preset--shadow--sharp)\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full is-resized ext-aspect-landscape\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"445\" src=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/image_2024-03-31_124209727.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-448\" style=\"width:417px;height:auto\" srcset=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/image_2024-03-31_124209727.png 800w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/image_2024-03-31_124209727-300x167.png 300w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/image_2024-03-31_124209727-768x427.png 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-flow wp-container-core-group-is-layout-18 wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\" style=\"margin-top:0;padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30)\">\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-foreground-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-8813c47eda5515be32ba9614f2d2014b\" style=\"font-size:clamp(0.984rem, 0.984rem + ((1vw - 0.2rem) * 0.645), 1.5rem);\"><strong>Shopping : n\u2019utilisez pas l\u2019app Temu, elle contient un spyware<\/strong>!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\"><strong>Date de Publication : 04 Octobre 2023<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\" style=\"font-size:clamp(14px, 0.875rem + ((1vw - 3.2px) * 0.156), 16px);\">Temu, appli populaire en France pour ses achats bon march\u00e9, cache un spyware collectant secr\u00e8tement donn\u00e9es personnelles, comme pr\u00e9f\u00e9rences de navigation et coordonn\u00e9es bancaires. Rapport de Grizzly Research expose ces pratiques malveillantes, soulignant autorisations douteuses demand\u00e9es. Malgr\u00e9 pertes financi\u00e8res, Temu pourrait exploiter donn\u00e9es \u00e0 fins lucratives. \u00c9vitez absolument d&rsquo;utiliser Temu pour prot\u00e9ger vos infos et s\u00e9curit\u00e9 en ligne.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-content-justification-center is-layout-flex wp-container-core-buttons-is-layout-9 wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-fill\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-background-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/www.it-connect.fr\/shopping-nutilisez-pas-lapp-temu-elle-contient-un-spyware\/\" style=\"border-radius:100px;background:linear-gradient(71deg,rgb(0,98,255) 0%,rgb(62,57,96) 100%)\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">En savoir plus<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column has-border-color has-palette-color-1-border-color is-layout-flow wp-container-core-column-is-layout-13 wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"border-width:5px;box-shadow:var(--wp--preset--shadow--sharp)\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full is-resized ext-aspect-landscape\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"445\" src=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image_2024-04-01_154508055.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-480\" style=\"width:413px;height:auto\" srcset=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image_2024-04-01_154508055.png 800w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image_2024-04-01_154508055-300x167.png 300w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image_2024-04-01_154508055-768x427.png 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-flow wp-container-core-group-is-layout-19 wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\" style=\"margin-top:0;padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30)\">\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-foreground-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-d13e7985e6ff1f7aac4c220cf705dbe7\" style=\"font-size:clamp(0.984rem, 0.984rem + ((1vw - 0.2rem) * 0.645), 1.5rem);\"><strong>Bing Chat : des publicit\u00e9s malveillantes rep\u00e9r\u00e9es dans les r\u00e9ponses du chatbot IA !<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\"><strong>Date de Publication : 29 Septembre 2023<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\" style=\"font-size:clamp(14px, 0.875rem + ((1vw - 3.2px) * 0.156), 16px);\">Des pirates ont r\u00e9ussi \u00e0 tromper Bing Chat, l&rsquo;assistant IA de Microsoft, en ins\u00e9rant de fausses publicit\u00e9s qui redirigeaient les utilisateurs vers un site malveillant distribuant un malware. Le nom de domaine du site malveillant \u00e9tait similaire \u00e0 celui du site officiel, ce qui a pi\u00e9g\u00e9 les utilisateurs. Le malware, potentiellement un info-stealer, n&rsquo;a pas encore \u00e9t\u00e9 identifi\u00e9. Cette situation souligne l&rsquo;importance de v\u00e9rifier les r\u00e9ponses des assistants IA et de rester vigilant en ligne.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-content-justification-center is-layout-flex wp-container-core-buttons-is-layout-10 wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-fill\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-background-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/www.it-connect.fr\/bing-chat-des-publicites-malveillantes-reperees-dans-les-reponses-du-chatbot-ia\/\" style=\"border-style:none;border-width:0px;border-radius:100px;background:linear-gradient(71deg,rgb(0,98,255) 0%,rgb(62,57,96) 100%)\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">En savoir plus<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Veille Technologique Qu&rsquo;est ce que la veille technologique ? : La veille technologique d\u00e9signe le processus syst\u00e9matique de surveillance, de collecte, d&rsquo;analyse et de diffusion d&rsquo;informations relatives aux avanc\u00e9es, aux innovations, et aux \u00e9volutions dans le domaine technologique. Elle vise \u00e0 anticiper les changements, \u00e0 d\u00e9tecter les opportunit\u00e9s et les menaces, ainsi qu&rsquo;\u00e0 rester inform\u00e9 [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-14","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"blocksy_meta":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/14","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=14"}],"version-history":[{"count":64,"href":"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/14\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":848,"href":"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/14\/revisions\/848"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=14"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}